"60:11:21" : {s: 60, a: 11, w: 21, r: "امن", t: "مُؤْمِنُونَ", l: "مُؤْمِن", lc: 202, tl: "mu'minūna", lb: "বিশ্বাসী ",e: "(are) believers", b: "ঈমানদার", f: 4, rm: "become/feel safe/secure, state of security/safety, trust, become quiet/tranquil in heart/mind, become free of expectation of evil or free of an object of dislike/hatred, promise/assurance of security/safety, become trustful/faithful/confident, to believe/acknowledge it, manifestation of humility/submission."},
